Anonymous Sat 29 Jun 2019 14:23:30 No.24006084 Report
Quoted By: >>24006122
I think I'm going to have to make a guide on how to create a general and put it on my pastebin when I have some spare time.

The newest or most recently updated stories go on top of the list. Only the first 13 or 14 writers stay on the list, the one at the bottom gets bumped off if a new story comes around or gets updated. Secondly we only put up stories on the pastebin list that posted on pastebin. We generally don't use any other sites. Thirdly, the writer themselves have to post it, we don't take green texts that have been posted on previous threads and put them into a pastebin ourselves. While admiral it is up to the authors themselves to make sure their work gets recognition if they so choose so.
